<p>This is a beautiful oil burner.  It is an unusual hexagonal shape and is black in colour with a grey flower pattern embossed on it. To use, simply place a tealight into the base and light carefully. Fill the oil well up to 2/3 full with water and then add a few of your favourite oil. Why not select an oil from our full range of essential &amp; fragrance oils! The oil burner stands approx 10cm tall.</p>